<h1>Kyle Stewart</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://kylestewart.co/now">kylestewart.co/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
San Diego
CA
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Software Developer at Pixite Apps <a href="http://pixiteapps.com">http://pixiteapps.com</a> + Maker <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maker_culture">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maker_culture</a>
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I reignite peoples belief in their personal creativity through entertaining and creative apps.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
Everyone is born creative, but so many of us lose confidence in our creativity - see <a href="http://www.brit.co/iamcreative/">http://www.brit.co/iamcreative/</a> The world is sorely lacking the creative thinking needed to solve problems big and small. I believe a creative and entertaining experience combined with positive social feedback can help reignite an individual’s creativity.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
How can I accomplish big things without first imagining big things?
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
So Good They Can’t Ignore You - Cal Newport
</p>

